race.comment: OOHLALOUVRE (9) stuck on gamely when resuming over this favoured course and trip. Strips fitter and looks one of the key hopes and carries a feather with the 3kg engaged. PANIGALE (4) resumes for a new yard after showing ability in Victoria. Trialled well enough and should be right in the mix fresh. TAKE A BOW (7) is racing better than her form reads and has a solid record at this track. At peak fitness now and capable of breaking through. SKY BLUE (10) continues to improve with racing and backs up quickly from a solid effort. Well drawn and has claims. WARILLA GORILLA (5) resumes off two trial wins and gets in light with the claim. Draws well and is a genuine winning chance fresh.
